WEBVTT

00:01:00.440 --> 00:01:03.616
I went into the villages
to work in rural India.

00:01:03.640 --> 00:01:06.416
I was part of land rights movement,

00:01:06.440 --> 00:01:07.936
farmers' movement

00:01:07.960 --> 00:01:09.320
and women's movement.

00:01:10.400 --> 00:01:11.696
On the same line,

00:01:11.720 --> 00:01:14.696
I ended up in a very small village,

00:01:14.720 --> 00:01:21.136
fell in love with a young, handsome,
dynamic young farmer-leader

00:01:21.160 --> 00:01:23.496
who was not very educated,

00:01:23.520 --> 00:01:25.856
but he could pull the crowd.

00:01:25.880 --> 00:01:28.456
And so in the passion of youth,

00:01:28.480 --> 00:01:30.336
I married him